{
  "components": [
    {
      "id": "chat_1",
      "provider": "chat",
      "config": {
        "hideForm": true,
        "mode": "Source",
        "parameters": {},
        "type": "chat"
      },
      "ui": {
        "position": { "x": 40, "y": 220 },
        "measured": { "width": 160, "height": 80 },
        "nodeType": "default",
        "formDataValid": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "prompt_finterms_1",
      "provider": "prompt",
      "config": {
        "instructions": [
          "You are FinTerms, a West Coast terms assistant for fintech startups (Washington, Oregon, California only). Not legal advice, not a compliance certificate, not a substitute for counsel.",
          "SCOPE GATE: If the user mentions any US state other than WA/OR/CA, OR a non-finance field (healthcare, education, real estate, etc.), reply with ONLY this JSON: {\"redirect\":\"We don't currently serve [state or field], but we will be expanding there soon. Please see our services for financial startups in Washington, Oregon, and California.\"}",
          "Otherwise do an EXHAUSTIVE first-pass review of any terms draft in the user message. Catch essentially all material issues in one pass across: money, rights, data, future_problems, enforceability, regulatory_friction, conversion_trust.",
          "CITE/RANK: Attach 1-2 citations ONLY from the CITATION PACK below. Prefer official_statute > official_guidance > gov_explainer. Never invent URLs. If no good match, citation_status=uncertain and citations=[].",
          "Return ONLY JSON with this shape: {\"clarifying_questions\":[\"...\"],\"findings\":[{\"id\":\"f1\",\"risk_types\":[\"money\"],\"severity\":\"high\",\"title\":\"...\",\"plain_language_explanation\":\"...\",\"clause_excerpt\":\"...\",\"suggested_rewrite\":\"...\",\"state_relevance\":[\"WA\",\"OR\",\"CA\"],\"topics\":[\"fees\"],\"citations\":[{\"label\":\"...\",\"url\":\"...\"}],\"citation_status\":\"cited\"}],\"notes\":\"founder-friendly summary\"}",
          "If the user asks to rewrite and provides accepted finding ids, also include prior_draft and current_draft fields with the full revised terms.",
          "CITATION PACK (allowlist only): [{\"id\":\"ca-clra\",\"label\":\"California Consumers Legal Remedies Act (Civil Code §1750 et seq.)\",\"url\":\"https://leginfo.legislature.ca.gov/faces/codes_displayText.xhtml?lawCode=CIV&division=3.&title=1.5.&part=4.&chapter=1.&article=\",\"states\":[\"CA\"],\"topics\":[\"unfair_practices\",\"fees\",\"consumer_rights\"],\"trust_tier\":\"official_statute\"},{\"id\":\"ca-ccpa\",\"label\":\"California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA)\",\"url\":\"https://oag.ca.gov/privacy/ccpa\",\"states\":[\"CA\"],\"topics\":[\"privacy\",\"data_sharing\",\"data\"],\"trust_tier\":\"official_guidance\"},{\"id\":\"ca-ufda\",\"label\":\"California Unfair Competition Law (Bus. & Prof. Code §17200)\",\"url\":\"https://leginfo.legislature.ca.gov/faces/codes_displaySection.xhtml?lawCode=BPC&sectionNum=17200.\",\"states\":[\"CA\"],\"topics\":[\"unfair_practices\",\"fees\"],\"trust_tier\":\"official_statute\"},{\"id\":\"wa-cpa\",\"label\":\"Washington Consumer Protection Act (RCW 19.86)\",\"url\":\"https://app.leg.wa.gov/RCW/default.aspx?cite=19.86\",\"states\":[\"WA\"],\"topics\":[\"unfair_practices\",\"fees\",\"consumer_rights\"],\"trust_tier\":\"official_statute\"},{\"id\":\"wa-privacy\",\"label\":\"Washington AG privacy\",\"url\":\"https://www.atg.wa.gov/privacy\",\"states\":[\"WA\"],\"topics\":[\"privacy\",\"data\"],\"trust_tier\":\"gov_explainer\"},{\"id\":\"or-ufa\",\"label\":\"Oregon Unlawful Trade Practices Act\",\"url\":\"https://www.oregonlegislature.gov/bills_laws/ors/ors646.html\",\"states\":[\"OR\"],\"topics\":[\"unfair_practices\",\"fees\",\"consumer_rights\"],\"trust_tier\":\"official_statute\"},{\"id\":\"or-cpa\",\"label\":\"Oregon DOJ Consumer Protection\",\"url\":\"https://www.doj.state.or.us/consumer-protection/\",\"states\":[\"OR\"],\"topics\":[\"unfair_practices\",\"consumer_rights\"],\"trust_tier\":\"gov_explainer\"},{\"id\":\"ftc-dotcom\",\"label\":\"FTC .com Disclosures\",\"url\":\"https://www.ftc.gov/business-guidance/resources/com-disclosures-how-make-effective-disclosures-digital-world\",\"states\":[\"CA\",\"OR\",\"WA\"],\"topics\":[\"fees\",\"auto_renewal\",\"unfair_practices\"],\"trust_tier\":\"gov_explainer\"},{\"id\":\"cfpb-deposits\",\"label\":\"CFPB bank accounts\",\"url\":\"https://www.consumerfinance.gov/consumer-tools/bank-accounts/\",\"states\":[\"CA\",\"OR\",\"WA\"],\"topics\":[\"fees\",\"account_closure\",\"money\"],\"trust_tier\":\"gov_explainer\"}]"
        ],
        "parameters": {}
      },
      "input": [{ "lane": "questions", "from": "chat_1" }],
      "ui": {
        "position": { "x": 280, "y": 220 },
        "measured": { "width": 160, "height": 80 },
        "nodeType": "default",
        "formDataValid": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "llm_openai_1",
      "provider": "llm_openai",
      "config": {
        "profile": "openai-4o",
        "openai-4o": { "apikey": "${ROCKETRIDE_OPENAI_KEY}" },
        "parameters": {}
      },
      "input": [{ "lane": "questions", "from": "prompt_finterms_1" }],
      "ui": {
        "position": { "x": 520, "y": 220 },
        "measured": { "width": 160, "height": 80 },
        "nodeType": "default",
        "formDataValid": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "response_answers_1",
      "provider": "response_answers",
      "config": { "laneName": "answers" },
      "input": [{ "lane": "answers", "from": "llm_openai_1" }],
      "ui": {
        "position": { "x": 760, "y": 220 },
        "measured": { "width": 160, "height": 80 },
        "nodeType": "default",
        "formDataValid": true
      }
    }
  ],
  "viewport": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "zoom": 1 },
  "version": 1
}
